QuestData.Title: Volrath Must Die
QuestData.Description:
The Horde are getting in our way of completing our mission here in Ashran. Their leader is High Warlord Volrath. He must be put down.
Push forth through the center road, enter Warspear and slay Volrath.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Volrath leads the Horde forces in Ashran.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay High Warlord Volrath found in the Horde base Warspear within Ashran.
